    "flock_note": "The Guru Bin transcendental companion to the factory Midnight Current preset. Where the factory preset has movement and darkness, this version adds the biological dimension — the living organisms pulsing at ocean wave frequency. CREATURE macro governs bio intensity. Let the bioRate of 0.12 Hz establish the groove.",
    "diagnosis": "bioRate=0.12 Hz: mapped to ocean wave frequency — this is the preset's rhythm engine. bioMix=0.4: significant bio presence, the organisms are active. bioBrightness=600 Hz: warm biological photophore color, not alien white. filterCutoff=250: mid-depth column, cold and dark but with organic warmth. lfo1Rate=0.12 Hz synchronized to bioRate."
